<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입 | 갓생 업</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<main class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <a href="/" class="link-dark text-decoration-none small">
                            ← 메인으로
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <p class="text-secondary text-uppercase small mb-2">Create Account</p>
                        <h1 class="h3 mb-2">회원가입</h1>
                        <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">입력 규칙에 맞게 정보를 작성해주세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-light border mb-4" role="alert">
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary">아이디: 영문/숫자 4~20자</div>
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary">닉네임: 한글/영문/숫자 최대 12자</div>
                        <div class="small text-body-secondary mb-0">비밀번호: 8~20자</div>
                    </div>

                    {{#formError}}
                        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                            {{formError}}
                        </div>
                    {{/formError}}

                    <form method="post" action="/auth/register">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{_csrf.parameterName}}" value="{{_csrf.token}}">

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="loginId" class="form-label">아이디</label>
                            <input id="loginId" type="text" name="loginId" value="{{registerRequest.loginId}}" class="form-control" placeholder="영문/숫자 4~20자" autocomplete="username" required>
                            {{#loginIdError}}
                                <div class="form-text text-danger">{{loginIdError}}</div>
                            {{/loginIdError}}
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="password" class="form-label">비밀번호</label>
                            <input id="password" type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="8~20자" autocomplete="new-password" required>
                            {{#passwordError}}
                                <div class="form-text text-danger">{{passwordError}}</div>
                            {{/passwordError}}
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="passwordConfirm" class="form-label">비밀번호 확인</label>
                            <input id="passwordConfirm" type="password" name="passwordConfirm" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호를 한 번 더 입력하세요" autocomplete="new-password" required>
                            {{#passwordConfirmError}}
                                <div class="form-text text-danger">{{passwordConfirmError}}</div>
                            {{/passwordConfirmError}}
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label for="nickname" class="form-label">닉네임</label>
                            <input id="nickname" type="text" name="nickname" value="{{registerRequest.nickname}}" class="form-control" placeholder="한글/영문/숫자 최대 12자" required>
                            {{#nicknameError}}
                                <div class="form-text text-danger">{{nicknameError}}</div>
                            {{/nicknameError}}
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-grid">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">회원가입</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>

                    <p class="text-center text-body-secondary mt-4 mb-0">
                        이미 계정이 있다면 <a href="/auth/login">로그인</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
